</para>
<para><bold>Alternative Formulations</bold><linebreak/>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>This weight is equal to the <ref refid="group__PkgWeightsRefTangentWeights" kindref="compound">Tangent Weight</ref>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>This weight is a special case of the <ref refid="group__PkgWeightsRefThreePointFamilyWeights" kindref="compound">Three Point Family Weight</ref>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>GeomTraits</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>a model of <computeroutput><ref refid="classAnalyticWeightTraits__2" kindref="compound">AnalyticWeightTraits_2</ref></computeroutput> for 2D points; a model of <computeroutput><ref refid="classAnalyticWeightTraits__3" kindref="compound">AnalyticWeightTraits_3</ref></computeroutput> for 3D points</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="pre"><para>(d * d1 + D1) != 0 &amp;&amp; (d * d2 + D2) != 0 </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
